    <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> handlers = events[typeEvent] || (events[typeEvent] = {});
    <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> previousFn = findHandler(handlers, originalHandler, delegation ? handler : <span class="hljs-literal">null</span>);

    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (previousFn) {
      previousFn.oneOff = previousFn.oneOff &amp;&amp; oneOff;
      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;
    }

    <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> uid = getUidEvent(originalHandler, originalTypeEvent.replace(namespaceRegex, <span class="hljs-string">''</span>));
    <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> fn = delegation ? bootstrapDelegationHandler(element, handler, delegationFn) : bootstrapHandler(element, handler);
    fn.delegationSelector = delegation ? handler : <span class="hljs-literal">null</span>;
    fn.originalHandler = originalHandler;
    fn.oneOff = oneOff;
    fn.uidEvent = uid;
    handlers[uid] = fn;
    element.addEventListener(typeEvent, fn, delegation);
  }

  <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title">removeHandler</span>(<span class="hljs-params">element, events, typeEvent, handler, delegationSelector</span>) </span>{
    <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> fn = findHandler(events[typeEvent], handler, delegationSelector);

    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!fn) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;
    }

    element.removeEventListener(typeEvent, fn, <span class="hljs-built_in">Boolean</span>(delegationSelector));
    <span class="hljs-keyword">delete</span> events[typeEvent][fn.uidEvent];
  }

  <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title">removeNamespacedHandlers</span>(<span class="hljs-params">element, events, typeEvent, namespace</span>) </span>{
    <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> storeElementEvent = events[typeEvent] || {};

      }
    });
  }

        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (data[config] === <span class="hljs-literal">undefined</span> || config.startsWith(<span class="hljs-string">'_'</span>) || config === <span class="hljs-string">'constructor'</span>) {

        }

        data[config](<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>);
      });
    }

  }

          <pre class="javascript">  <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> NODE_TEXT = <span class="hljs-number">3</span>;
  <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> SelectorEngine = {
    find(selector, element = <span class="hljs-built_in">document</span>.documentElement) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> [].concat(...Element.prototype.querySelectorAll.call(element, selector));
    },

    findOne(selector, element = <span class="hljs-built_in">document</span>.documentElement) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> Element.prototype.querySelector.call(element, selector);
    },

    children(element, selector) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> [].concat(...element.children).filter(<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-params">child</span> =&gt;</span> child.matches(selector));
    },

    parents(element, selector) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> parents = [];
      <span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> ancestor = element.parentNode;

      <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (ancestor &amp;&amp; ancestor.nodeType === Node.ELEMENT_NODE &amp;&amp; ancestor.nodeType !== NODE_TEXT) {
        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (ancestor.matches(selector)) {
          parents.push(ancestor);
        }

        ancestor = ancestor.parentNode;
      }

      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> parents;
    },

    prev(element, selector) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> previous = element.previousElementSibling;

      <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (previous) {
        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (previous.matches(selector)) {
          <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> [previous];
        }

        previous = previous.previousElementSibling;
      }

      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> [];
    },

    next(element, selector) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> next = element.nextElementSibling;

      <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (next) {
        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (next.matches(selector)) {
          <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> [next];
        }

        next = next.nextElementSibling;
      }

      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> [];
    },

    focusableChildren(element) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> focusables = [<span class="hljs-string">'a'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'button'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'input'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'textarea'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'select'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'details'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'[tabindex]'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'[contenteditable="true"]'</span>].map(<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-params">selector</span> =&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-string">`<span class="hljs-subst">${selector}</span>:not([tabindex^="-"])`</span>).join(<span class="hljs-string">', '</span>);

    <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> carouselInterface(element, config) {

        data.to(config);
      } <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">typeof</span> action === <span class="hljs-string">'string'</span>) {

        }

        data[action]();

        data.pause();
        data.cycle();
      }

    <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> dataApiClickHandler(event) {

    rect.y = rect.top;

  <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title">getClippingRect</span>(<span class="hljs-params">element, boundary, rootBoundary</span>) </span>{
    <span class="hljs-keyword">var</span> mainClippingParents = boundary === <span class="hljs-string">'clippingParents'</span> ? getClippingParents(element) : [].concat(boundary);
    <span class="hljs-keyword">var</span> clippingParents = [].concat(mainClippingParents, [rootBoundary]);
    <span class="hljs-keyword">var</span> firstClippingParent = clippingParents[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>];
    <span class="hljs-keyword">var</span> clippingRect = clippingParents.reduce(<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> (<span class="hljs-params">accRect, clippingParent</span>) </span>{
      <span class="hljs-keyword">var</span> rect = getClientRectFromMixedType(element, clippingParent);
      accRect.top = max(rect.top, accRect.top);
      accRect.right = min(rect.right, accRect.right);
      accRect.bottom = min(rect.bottom, accRect.bottom);
      accRect.left = max(rect.left, accRect.left);
      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> accRect;
    }, getClientRectFromMixedType(element, firstClippingParent));
    clippingRect.width = clippingRect.right - clippingRect.left;
    clippingRect.height = clippingRect.bottom - clippingRect.top;

    clippingRect.y = clippingRect.top;
    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> clippingRect;
  }

  <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title">computeOffsets</span>(<span class="hljs-params">_ref</span>) </span>{
    <span class="hljs-keyword">var</span> reference = _ref.reference,
        element = _ref.element,
        placement = _ref.placement;
    <span class="hljs-keyword">var</span> basePlacement = placement ? getBasePlacement(placement) : <span class="hljs-literal">null</span>;
    <span class="hljs-keyword">var</span> variation = placement ? getVariation(placement) : <span class="hljs-literal">null</span>;
    <span class="hljs-keyword">var</span> commonX = reference.x + reference.width / <span class="hljs-number">2</span> - element.width / <span class="hljs-number">2</span>;
    <span class="hljs-keyword">var</span> commonY = reference.y + reference.height / <span class="hljs-number">2</span> - element.height / <span class="hljs-number">2</span>;
    <span class="hljs-keyword">var</span> offsets;

    <span class="hljs-keyword">switch</span> (basePlacement) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> top:
        offsets = {
          <span class="hljs-attr">x</span>: commonX,
          <span class="hljs-attr">y</span>: reference.y - element.height
        };
        <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>;

      <span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> bottom:
        offsets = {
          <span class="hljs-attr">x</span>: commonX,
          <span class="hljs-attr">y</span>: reference.y + reference.height
        };
        <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>;

      <span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> right:
        offsets = {
          <span class="hljs-attr">x</span>: reference.x + reference.width,
          <span class="hljs-attr">y</span>: commonY
        };
        <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>;

      <span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> left:
        offsets = {
          <span class="hljs-attr">x</span>: reference.x - element.width,
          <span class="hljs-attr">y</span>: commonY
        };
        <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>;

      <span class="hljs-keyword">default</span>:
        offsets = {
          <span class="hljs-attr">x</span>: reference.x,
          <span class="hljs-attr">y</span>: reference.y
        };
    }

    <span class="hljs-keyword">var</span> mainAxis = basePlacement ? getMainAxisFromPlacement(basePlacement) : <span class="hljs-literal">null</span>;

    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (mainAxis != <span class="hljs-literal">null</span>) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">var</span> len = mainAxis === <span class="hljs-string">'y'</span> ? <span class="hljs-string">'height'</span> : <span class="hljs-string">'width'</span>;

      <span class="hljs-keyword">switch</span> (variation) {
        <span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> start:
          offsets[mainAxis] = offsets[mainAxis] - (reference[len] / <span class="hljs-number">2</span> - element[len] / <span class="hljs-number">2</span>);
          <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>;

        <span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> end:
          offsets[mainAxis] = offsets[mainAxis] + (reference[len] / <span class="hljs-number">2</span> - element[len] / <span class="hljs-number">2</span>);
          <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>;
      }
    }

    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> offsets;
  }

      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._resolvePossibleFunction(title);
    }

    updateAttachment(attachment) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (attachment === <span class="hljs-string">'right'</span>) {
        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-string">'end'</span>;
      }

      <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (attachment === <span class="hljs-string">'left'</span>) {
        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-string">'start'</span>;
      }

      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> attachment;
    } <span class="hljs-comment">// Private</span>


    _initializeOnDelegatedTarget(event, context) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> context || <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>.constructor.getOrCreateInstance(event.delegateTarget, <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._getDelegateConfig());
    }

    _getOffset() {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> {
        offset
      } = <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._config;

      <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">typeof</span> offset === <span class="hljs-string">'string'</span>) {
        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> offset.split(<span class="hljs-string">','</span>).map(<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-params">val</span> =&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">Number</span>.parseInt(val, <span class="hljs-number">10</span>));
      }

      <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">typeof</span> offset === <span class="hljs-string">'function'</span>) {
        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-params">popperData</span> =&gt;</span> offset(popperData, <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element);
      }

      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> offset;
    }

    _resolvePossibleFunction(content) {

    }

    _getPopperConfig(attachment) {

    _addAttachmentClass(attachment) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>.getTipElement().classList.add(<span class="hljs-string">`<span class="hljs-subst">${<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._getBasicClassPrefix()}</span>-<span class="hljs-subst">${<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>.updateAttachment(attachment)}</span>`</span>);
    }

    _getAttachment(placement) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> AttachmentMap[placement.toUpperCase()];
    }

    _setListeners() {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> triggers = <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._config.trigger.split(<span class="hljs-string">' '</span>);

      triggers.forEach(<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-params">trigger</span> =&gt;</span> {
        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (trigger === <span class="hljs-string">'click'</span>) {
          EventHandler.on(<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element, <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>.constructor.Event.CLICK, <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._config.selector, event =&gt; <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>.toggle(event));
        } <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (trigger !== TRIGGER_MANUAL) {
          <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> eventIn = trigger === TRIGGER_HOVER ? <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>.constructor.Event.MOUSEENTER : <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>.constructor.Event.FOCUSIN;
          <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> eventOut = trigger === TRIGGER_HOVER ? <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>.constructor.Event.MOUSELEAVE : <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>.constructor.Event.FOCUSOUT;
          EventHandler.on(<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element, eventIn, <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._config.selector, event =&gt; <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._enter(event));
          EventHandler.on(<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element, eventOut, <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._config.selector, event =&gt; <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._leave(event));
        }
      });

      <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._hideModalHandler = <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-params">()</span> =&gt;</span> {
        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element) {
          <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>.hide();
        }
      };

      EventHandler.on(<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element.closest(SELECTOR_MODAL), EVENT_MODAL_HIDE, <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._hideModalHandler);

      <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._config.selector) {
        <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._config = { ...this._config,
          <span class="hljs-attr">trigger</span>: <span class="hljs-string">'manual'</span>,
          <span class="hljs-attr">selector</span>: <span class="hljs-string">''</span>
        };
      } <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> {
        <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._fixTitle();
      }
    }

    _fixTitle() {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> title = <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element.getAttribute(<span class="hljs-string">'title'</span>);

      <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> originalTitleType = <span class="hljs-keyword">typeof</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element.getAttribute(<span class="hljs-string">'data-bs-original-title'</span>);

      <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (title || originalTitleType !== <span class="hljs-string">'string'</span>) {
        <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element.setAttribute(<span class="hljs-string">'data-bs-original-title'</span>, title || <span class="hljs-string">''</span>);

        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (title &amp;&amp; !<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element.getAttribute(<span class="hljs-string">'aria-label'</span>) &amp;&amp; !<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element.textContent) {
          <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element.setAttribute(<span class="hljs-string">'aria-label'</span>, title);
        }

        <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element.setAttribute(<span class="hljs-string">'title'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">''</span>);
      }
    }

    _enter(event, context) {
      context = <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._initializeOnDelegatedTarget(event, context);

      <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (event) {
        context._activeTrigger[event.type === <span class="hljs-string">'focusin'</span> ? TRIGGER_FOCUS : TRIGGER_HOVER] = <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>;
      }

      <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (context.getTipElement().classList.contains(CLASS_NAME_SHOW$<span class="hljs-number">2</span>) || context._hoverState === HOVER_STATE_SHOW) {
        context._hoverState = HOVER_STATE_SHOW;
        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;
      }

      clearTimeout(context._timeout);
      context._hoverState = HOVER_STATE_SHOW;

      <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!context._config.delay || !context._config.delay.show) {
        context.show();
        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;
      }

      context._timeout = setTimeout(<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-params">()</span> =&gt;</span> {
        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (context._hoverState === HOVER_STATE_SHOW) {
          context.show();
        }
      }, context._config.delay.show);
    }

    _leave(event, context) {
      context = <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._initializeOnDelegatedTarget(event, context);

      <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (event) {
        context._activeTrigger[event.type === <span class="hljs-string">'focusout'</span> ? TRIGGER_FOCUS : TRIGGER_HOVER] = context._element.contains(event.relatedTarget);
      }

      <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (context._isWithActiveTrigger()) {
        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;
      }

      clearTimeout(context._timeout);
      context._hoverState = HOVER_STATE_OUT;

      <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!context._config.delay || !context._config.delay.hide) {
        context.hide();
        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;
      }

      context._timeout = setTimeout(<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-params">()</span> =&gt;</span> {
        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (context._hoverState === HOVER_STATE_OUT) {
          context.hide();
        }
      }, context._config.delay.hide);
    }

    _isWithActiveTrigger() {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> trigger <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._activeTrigger) {
        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._activeTrigger[trigger]) {
          <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>;
        }
      }

      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-literal">false</span>;
    }

    _getConfig(config) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> dataAttributes = Manipulator.getDataAttributes(<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element);

    }

        <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._maybeScheduleHide();

    hide() {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element.classList.contains(CLASS_NAME_SHOW)) {

    _getConfig(config) {

    _maybeScheduleHide() {

    _onInteraction(event, isInteracting) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">switch</span> (event.type) {

        <span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> <span class="hljs-string">'mouseout'</span>:
          <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._hasMouseInteraction = isInteracting;
          <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>;

        <span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> <span class="hljs-string">'focusin'</span>:
        <span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> <span class="hljs-string">'focusout'</span>:
          <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._hasKeyboardInteraction = isInteracting;
          <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>;
      }

      <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (isInteracting) {

      }

      <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> nextElement = event.relatedTarget;

      <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element === nextElement || <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element.contains(nextElement)) {
        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;
      }

      <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._maybeScheduleHide();
    }

    _setListeners() {
      EventHandler.on(<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element, EVENT_MOUSEOVER, event =&gt; <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._onInteraction(event, <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>));
      EventHandler.on(<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element, EVENT_MOUSEOUT, event =&gt; <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._onInteraction(event, <span class="hljs-literal">false</span>));
      EventHandler.on(<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element, EVENT_FOCUSIN, event =&gt; <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._onInteraction(event, <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>));
      EventHandler.on(<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._element, EVENT_FOCUSOUT, event =&gt; <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._onInteraction(event, <span class="hljs-literal">false</span>));
    }

    _clearTimeout() {
      clearTimeout(<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._timeout);
      <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>._timeout = <span class="hljs-literal">null</span>;
    } <span class="hljs-comment">// Static</span>


    <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> jQueryInterface(config) {
      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>.each(<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> (<span class="hljs-params"></span>) </span>{
        <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> data = Toast.getOrCreateInstance(<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>, config);

        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">typeof</span> config === <span class="hljs-string">'string'</span>) {
          <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">typeof</span> data[config] === <span class="hljs-string">'undefined'</span>) {
            <span class="hljs-keyword">throw</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">TypeError</span>(<span class="hljs-string">`No method named "<span class="hljs-subst">${config}</span>"`</span>);
          }

          data[config](<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>);
        }
      });
    }

  }

  enableDismissTrigger(Toast);
